<title>MY SAVIOUR'S LOVE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A hehpihna thu genthiem leng,
 Nazareth Isu ngei kha;
 Tibang lawma ei hehpih in,
 Gilo thiem ei chansak tai.

[V2]
 A mak na e! A mak na e!
 Kumsawta ka la hi he'n;
 A mak na e! A mak na e!
 Hukdampa ei hehpihna.

[V3]
 2. Huonah kei dingin A paucham,
 Kei thu hilo Nang thu ti'n;
 Amah di'n A mitthi pawtlo,
 A ul thisan va'i keidi'n.

[V4]
 3. Angelte'n lungsiet a veng ui,
 Khawvel vak apat hungin;
 Ka tha di'n A lungkham puokgik,
 Chu lungmuon di'n a hung ui.

[V5]
 4. Ka gitloh lungkham A lamang,
 Amah a guola bawlin;
 Puokgik chuh Kalvari a puo'n,
 Ama'n A thuokin A thii.

[V6]
 5. Tatsa tawh lopi taka um,
 Amel chuh ka muh tieng leh;
 Ka kumsawt kipahna hi'na,
 Ei hehpih la a sak chuh.</lyrics>
</song>